          "contents": "from neighborhood import Painter\n# ADD import custom BELOW\n\njulian = Painter()\n\n# ADD DEFINITION FOR collect_and_move FUNCTION IN custom.py\n \n\n\n# Move through the Neighborhood using the collect_and_move function",
